{"lemma":"نَحْسُ","slug":"نَحْسُ","root":"ن.ح.س","root_slug":"ن-ح-س","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ح-س","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"نَحْس","root":"نحس","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n39500","n39503","n39504"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%92%D8%B3%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to bring bad luck, to jinx, to hex"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of نَحَسَ (naḥasa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"bad luck, misfortune"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Cognate with Classical Syriac ܢܚܫܐ and Hebrew נחש."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n39500","headword_ar":"نَحِسَ","root":"nHs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, A, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHusa","text_ar":"نَحُسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHisu","text_ar":"نَحِسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like [its contr.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suEida","text_ar":"سُعِدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Bd, xvii. 30;) inf. n. [of the first]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHasN","text_ar":"نَحَسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [of the second"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuHuwsapN","text_ar":"نُحُوسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, unprosperous, unfortunate, inauspicious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unlucky:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K:) said of a man, (A, Bd,) and of a star, (TA,) or other thing. (S, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","K","Bd","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n39503","headword_ar":"نَحْسٌ","root":"nHs","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Unprosperousness, unfortunateness, inauspiciousness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unluckiness; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saEodN","text_ar":"سَعْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, A, K;) of stars, and of other things: pl. [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anoHusN","text_ar":"اَنْحُسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuHuwsN","text_ar":"نُحُوسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manaAHisu","text_ar":"مَنَاحِسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is an irreg. pl. of the same, (TA,) syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$aAy^imu","text_ar":"مَشَايِمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IDrd, K, TA,) which is in like manner an irreg. pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uw^omN","text_ar":"شُوْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [In Har, p."},{"kind":"text","text":"375"},{"kind":"text","text":", a doubt is expressed respecting"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manaAHisu","text_ar":"مَنَاحِسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as to its being a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHosN","text_ar":"نَحْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but only from ignorance of their being any authority for its being so: it may, however, be pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manoHasapN","text_ar":"مَنْحَسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and not of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHosN","text_ar":"نَحْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] In the Kur, [liv. 19,] some read,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fY yawomi naHosK","text_ar":"فى يَوْمِ نَحْسٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In a day of unprosperousness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: others read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nHs","text_ar":"نحس"},{"kind":"text","text":"as an epithet. (S.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHisN","text_ar":"نَحِسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  Also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Difficulty, distress, trouble,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fatigue; harm, injury,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil state"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahodN","text_ar":"جَهْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dur~N","text_ar":"ضُرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anoHusN","text_ar":"اَنْحُسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","IDrd","K"]},{"entry_id":"n39504","headword_ar":"نَحِسٌ","root":"nHs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHosN","text_ar":"نَحْسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHiysN","text_ar":"نَحِيسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHuwsN","text_ar":"نَحُوسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"munoHuwsN","text_ar":"مُنْحُوسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Unprosperous, unfortunate, inauspicious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unlucky."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN naHisN","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ نَحِسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHosN","text_ar":"نَحْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manoHuwsN","text_ar":"مَنْحُوسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An unprosperous man"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: pl. of the last,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manaAHiysu","text_ar":"مَنَاحِيسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomN naHosN","text_ar":"يَوْمٌ نَحْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, TA) [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHisN","text_ar":"نَحِسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHuwsN","text_ar":"نَحُوسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHiysN","text_ar":"نَحِيسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manoHuwsN","text_ar":"مَنْحُوسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An unprosperous day"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and in the pl.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ay~aAmN naHosN","text_ar":"اَيَّامٌ نَحْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [which seems to indicate that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHosN","text_ar":"نَحْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is originally an inf. n.,] (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHosapN","text_ar":"نَحْسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHosaAtN","text_ar":"نَحْسَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHosapN","text_ar":"نَحْسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Az, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHisapN","text_ar":"نَحِسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) and [its pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHisaAtN","text_ar":"نَحِسَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHiysapN","text_ar":"نَحِيسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K.) [and app. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAHisapN","text_ar":"نَاحِسَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":",] and [its pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nawaAHisu","text_ar":"نَوَاحِسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) In the Kur, [liv. 19,] some read, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY yawomK naHosK","text_ar":"فِى يَوْمٍ نَحْسٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In an unprosperous day"},{"kind":"text","text":"], as well as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY yawomi naHosK","text_ar":"فِى يَوْمِ نَحْسٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, TA:) and AA reads [in the Kur, xli. 15,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY A^ay~aAmK naHosaAtK","text_ar":"فِى اَيَّامٍ نَحْسَاتٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHisaAtK","text_ar":"نَحِسَاتٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is another reading. (TA.) You also say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmN naAHisN","text_ar":"عَامٌ نَاحِسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHiysN","text_ar":"نَحِيسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A year of dearth"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drought"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sterility:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, K:) so they assert. (IDrd.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aHosaAni","text_ar":"النَّحْسَانِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is an appellation of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The two planets Saturn and Mars:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, K:) like as [the contr.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~aEodaAni","text_ar":"السَّعْدَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied to Venus and Mercury. (Ibn-'Abbád.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","K","TA","Az","IDrd"]}]}}